Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This school has seven wonders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Four" "Five" "Six" "Seven"\N"One" "Two" "Three"\NYou haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Four" "Five" "Six" "Seven"\N"One" "Two" "Three"\NThen I'll tell you about one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll tell you about one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The most famous story...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seven"\NThe most famous story...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seven"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Seven"\N...is the seventh of the Seven Wonders:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}san {\i0}of the Bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the third stall in the girls' bathroom\Non the third floor of the old building...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Girls' Bathroom"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Girls' Bathroom"\N...lives Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}, who grants a wish\Nto anyone who summons her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...lives Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}, who grants a wish\Nto anyone who summons her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But in exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.70,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,she takes something precious from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To call her, knock three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}, Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:01:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A see-through body,\Nan old uniform, ghostly orbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're a...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an apparition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The seventh of the Seven Wonders of the School,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hanako-{\i1}san {\i0}of the Bathroom."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Toilet-bound Hanako-kun"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Apparition 1: Hanako-{\i1}san {\i0}of the Bathroom"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Girls' Bathroom"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Girls' Bathroom"\NY-You're Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your bob cut? And your red skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's stuff's out of fashion these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fashion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call me Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a boy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a boy, but the rest of\Nthe rumors you heard are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I grant a wish for whoever summons me\Nand take one thing as payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...not just some perverted ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy Hanako-{\i1}san {\i0}is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, tell me your name and your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's simpler than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yashiro Nene, high school,\Nfirst year, class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"YASHIRO: LOVE"\NI'm Yashiro Nene, high school,\Nfirst year, class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"YASHIRO: LOVE"\NI want the person I like to\Nreturn my feelings right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"YASHIRO: LOVE"\NYashiro, huh? And you want success in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"YASHIRO: LOVE"\NWho with?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Minamoto-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, in second year!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's amazing! Cool, smart,\Nand nice to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I dropped my pencil case\Nand he picked it up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stare"\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you grant wishes, Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Success"\NHow do you grant wishes, Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Success"\NDo you use special items or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. I've got a great one right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"100 Methods of Love: This is Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"100 Methods of Love: This is Love"\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"A how-to book"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--No.\N--Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you borrow my power,\Nyou need to pay a fitting price.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want power beyond human comprehension,\Nthe price will be that much steeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what if I said I still wanted more?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...impossible, since I haven't\Ngot the tools for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But this will work out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"High hopes"\NBut this will work out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"High hopes"\NHanako-{\i1}san {\i0}is a ghost who grants wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"High hopes"\NHe must have granted love wishes\Nlots of times before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"High hopes"\NMethod 78: Make the most of your special skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any special skills, Yashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A field!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our school's practice garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the gardening club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"TA-DA!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"TA-DA!"\NMy special skill is gardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dirt..."\NWhat's that look for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dirt..."\NI grow flowers, too! I'm plenty feminine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I started gardening
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,because a boy I used to have a crush on\Nsaid that he liked "feminine" girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I also started cooking and sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to tell him I liked him\Nonce I was good at all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you start liking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Since right after I started junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I confessed my feelings to him a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:06:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"SHOCK"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"SHOCK"\NThat's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, you're not my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not into fat daikon legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikon legs... Daikon... Daikon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was a month ago!\NI'm totally over it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm totally obsessed with Minamoto-{\i1}senpai {\i0}now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get a wonderful person like him to return\Nmy love and prove I'm too good for that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyone would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, but I bet you don't\Nknow much about Minamoto-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, what's his first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a bug. I should feed it to the carp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A message card?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Love"\NYup. Give your {\i1}senpai {\i0}this\Nalong with something you grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Love"\NI call it Operation: Present!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Love"\NHow literal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've tried before and--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't know if it'll turn out\Nthe same until you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, make the most of what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've put in all this hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I feel like confessing my feelings\Nwould be too sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped your pencil case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write him a thank you for picking up\Nmy pencil case the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dazzling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Yashiro, what do you grow here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Minamoto, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There are summer vegetables on your desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you for the other day."\NThere are summer vegetables on your desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you for the other day."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you save a fox or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's turned into a weird mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Mermaid"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Operation: Summer Vegetables\Nwas a good idea. It had the element of surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not! It was a failure the minute\Nthey thought it was a fox returning a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A daikon returning a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's been talking to herself for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the heat's gotten to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough. I'm going to quit gardening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't be hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:10:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got other talents,\Nso let's switch to those.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Enthusiasm is all well and good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Operation: Button of Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I found an opening and grabbed one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sew it back on and boost his affection!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Minamoto-{\i1}senp{\i0}--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Minamoto-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you're missing a button!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Use one of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,--No, mine!\N--No, one of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's going to be\NMinamoto-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s button!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Operation: Boxed Lunch"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Make him a boxed lunch\Nwith your summer vegetables!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal lunch would be boring,\Nso make them look like cute characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Chop, chop"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Chop, chop"\N"Sizzle"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that from a girl? You lucky devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could have...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think someone forgot this.\NI'll bring it to the lost and found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:11:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I overdid it! Another failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Operation: Corner of Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold a piece of toast in your mouth\Nand bump into him as he turns a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Run out when I give the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Now!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what I'll say to-- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kou?! Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, someone just went flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell down those stairs! Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who did I run into?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambulance! Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Girls' Bathroom"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,None of this is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that last one had\Nnothing to do with my talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, this is all too roundabout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,why not just tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. I'm a beginner at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only thing left I can think to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A beginner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not many people can or do summon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder I thought something was off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plans were way too normal\Nand wholesome for a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me, wholesome Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grrrrr"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grrrrr"\NI-I have unwholesome items, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grrrrr"\NLike, let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}kokeshi {\i0}doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little bit sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was so sure I was going to get my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did the window have to be open?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Seal"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Hanako-{\i1}san {\i0}drop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}, what are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, those are matchmaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Matchmaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Yashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain! Explain or I'll swallow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are mermaid scales.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who swallow those scales
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,will be cursed, but also united by a strong--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gulp"\Nwill be cursed, but also united by a strong--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gulp"\NYashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"Panic, panic"\NYashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Panic, panic"\NI said not to swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Panic, panic"\NYou'll be cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Panic, panic"\NI don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If it means Minamoto-{\i1}senpai {\i0}will\Nreturn my feelings, I don't mind being cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You did have the right items after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:13:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Slender legs"\N...don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Slender legs"\NU-Umm... Minamoto-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Blushing"\NU-Umm... Minamoto-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've liked you ever since first year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Say no, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've liked her for a long time,\Nand I wouldn't want to be with anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai has someone he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But as long as I have this, that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyone would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked so hard, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I barely even talked to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even try to tell him my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've put in all this hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But what was I working toward?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I put in misguided effort and\Nconvinced myself it would pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I even resorted to this thing. I'm so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It serves me right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A little longer and you would have dried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got everything ready for you, Yashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I a fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? It comes with a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under the Mermaid's Curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish are the mermaid's servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd gotten someone else to eat a scale,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the curse would be split between you\Nand you wouldn't turn into a fish completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You would turn kind of fishlike, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Ugh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid scales just curse whoever swallows them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're only called matchmaking charms
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because people under the same curse\Nshare a special bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't use it, did you? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized I don't love Senpai at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just using him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you said, Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}, anyone would do\Nas long as they returned my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that was my real wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What have we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are truly foolish creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But rejoice, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you will serve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you the utmost kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A fish with a face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here to collect you, her new servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're obstructing my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my way, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My life spans millennia. A mere School Wonder\Ncould never hope to best me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--Wait a second.\N--Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't granted one of that girl's wishes yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to take her,\Ncould you wait until I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! Do not presume to command me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll use force, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What impudence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:19:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How can an apparition\Na paltry few decades old be so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, School Wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to send her packing for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but she seems persistent,\Nso she'll probably be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess buying some time is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that fish going to take me away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd never made that wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying won't save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what happens when you\Nget mixed up with apparitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you not to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I went out of my way to warn you, didn't I,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you big dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But you didn't use this on your {\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:20:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That means I can still grant you a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be human again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's your wish, I'll grant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For a price, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What kind of price?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? But I'll let you lead\Nthe bare minimum of a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll turn back! I want to turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}, make me human again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you pay me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,with your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With my... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the border between this life\Nand the next, we have been linked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll minimize the curse's effect on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, I'll take...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...your labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a relief. I was just thinking\NI wanted a human assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think I meant something dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yashiro, you naughty daikon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I can touch you, Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told you, we share a bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I did grant you two wishes, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted someone, anyone,\Nto return your feelings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And as far as you're concerned, sharing a bond\Nwith someone is the same thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was how I met...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...an unearthly boy apparition in a classroom\Nlit by the red rays of twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, also, those will get better if you dry them.
